videos.headline: Lewerke avoids pressure then throws TD pass
videos.description: Brian Lewerke escapes pressure and throws a 6-yard touchdown pass to Cody White as he is taken down to put Michigan State up early.

videos.headline: White hauls in 60-yard pass for the Spartans
videos.description: Brian Lewerke's deep pass is caught by Cody White for a gain of 60-yards to put the Spartans in the red zone.

videos.headline: Spartan defense forces early turnover
videos.description: Ramaud Chiaokhiao-Bowman hauls in a pass but he loses the ball as he hits the ground and the call is overturned giving Michigan State the ball.

videos.headline: Northwestern defense comes up with big sack
videos.description: Northwestern brings the blitz and Brian Lewerke is sacked by Joe Gaziano for a loss of 10 yards forcing the Spartans to punt.

videos.headline: Northwestern gets on the board with short TD
videos.description: Clayton Thorson keeps it and gets the push in to the end zone for a touchdown to cut Michigan State's lead.

videos.headline: Dantonio wants to see ball security in second half
videos.description: Michigan State head coach Mark Dantonio says his offense can't turn the ball over in the second half and the defense needs to continue to stop the run to have success.

videos.headline: Spartan defense gets to Thorson
videos.description: Clayton Thorson is sacked by Khari Willis for a loss of 1 yard forcing the Wildcats to punt at the start of the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Northwestern takes lead with trick play TD
videos.description: Clayton Thorson hands it off to running back Justin Jackson who then completes a 12-yard touchdown pass to Bennett Skowronek to give the Wildcats the lead.

videos.headline: Lewerke with great throw on the move
videos.description: Brian Lewerke is forced out of the pocket but he finds Cody White down field for a gain of 45 yards putting the Spartans in Wildcat territory.

videos.headline: Michigan State trails Northwestern after missed FG
videos.description: Matt Coghlin attempts a 32-yard field goal hitting the upright for the second time today and it is no good. Spartans trail the Wildcats with six minutes to play.

videos.headline: Spartans score tying TD with 25 seconds left
videos.description: Brian Lewerke finds Felton Davis III in the corner of the end zone for a 13-yard touchdown to tie the game with 25 seconds left.

videos.headline: Northwestern strikes first in OT
videos.description: Clayton Thorson connects with Cameron Green for a 14-yard touchdown to give Northwestern the lead in over time.

videos.headline: Michigan State answers with 6-yard TD
videos.description: Brian Lewerke throws a 6-yard pass to Felton Davis III in the end zone to send the game into 2nd overtime.

videos.headline: White hauls in 11-yard TD pass in 2nd OT
videos.description: Brian Lewerke finds Cody White in the back of the end zone for 11-yard touchdown to give the Spartans the lead.

videos.headline: Jackson scores for Northwestern in 2nd OT
videos.description: Justin Jackson runs up the middle and scores from the 3-yard line to send the game to 3rd overtime.

videos.headline: Northwestern scores in 3rd OT
videos.description: Clayton Thorson's pass is caught by Flynn Nagel who runs along the sideline into the end zone in 3rd OT.

videos.headline: Northwestern picks off Lewerke in the end zone to win in 3rd OT
videos.description: Brian Lewerke is intercpeted in the end zone by Nate Hall to give Northwestern the win in 3rd overtime.

videos.headline: Northwestern turned up the offense to upset Michigan State in 3rd OT
videos.description: Ahmad Brooks and Anish Shroff break down how Northwestern's offense was the key in their 39-31 upset of Michigan State in third overtime.

videos.headline: Northwestern wins in dramatic 3OT  fashion
videos.description: Clayton Thorson throws for 356 yards and leads the Wildcats to a 39-31 victory over No. 16 Michigan State.
